.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"We define `𝓞_ℂ_[p]` as the subring of elements of `ℂ_[p]` with valuation `≤ 1`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.html#«term𝓞_ℂ_[_]»","kind":"def","line":213,"name":"«term𝓞_ℂ_[_]»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.lean#L213-L214"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.html#PadicComplexInt\"><span class=\"name\">PadicComplexInt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">hp</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/Basic.html#Fact\">Fact</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Nat/Prime/Defs.html#Nat.Prime\">Nat.Prime</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span>)</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Valuation/ValuationSubring.html#ValuationSubring\">ValuationSubring</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.html#PadicComplex\">ℂ_[</a><span class=\"fn\">p</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.html#PadicComplex\">]</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"We define `𝓞_ℂ_[p]` as the valuation subring of `ℂ_[p]`, consisting of those elements with\nvaluation `≤ 1`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.html#PadicComplexInt","kind":"def","line":209,"name":"PadicComplexInt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/NumberTheory/Padics/Complex.lean#L209-L211"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_ki